%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a49675d3da19b054686ae9ecd58461ad, type: 3}
  m_Name: FirstInteractionShop
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  lines:
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: "\u2026Oh. You\u2019re\u2026 kind of cute."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a732a571f82d164eaae6405497a3c69, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dfd49278aaeff4b4a9423e9a4dedf194, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 40eddda1543e24346865a91cacd547f2, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: Cute? Seriously?
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1a1f0c89fd2ad8f488fa25619df9f084, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 40eddda1543e24346865a91cacd547f2, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: "I\u2019m wearing a life support helmet, rookie. Not a fashion accessory."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c048e118567af15419bcdcc777d7bf53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 40eddda1543e24346865a91cacd547f2, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: "I mean... just the look. The coat, the hat, the little drone\u2026 it\u2019s
      unexpected."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a732a571f82d164eaae6405497a3c69, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c048e118567af15419bcdcc777d7bf53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ae6777ac6a52f3340b37a7632bbd4eb9, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: "Great. First outsider I meet in weeks and she thinks I\u2019m adorable."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c048e118567af15419bcdcc777d7bf53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ae6777ac6a52f3340b37a7632bbd4eb9, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: So you know about the energy these creatures carry.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a732a571f82d164eaae6405497a3c69, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: c048e118567af15419bcdcc777d7bf53, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: Of course I do. Creatures out here are full of fractured resonance. You
      take them down, they drop Xenocore Elements. Raw stuff. Valuable.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dfd49278aaeff4b4a9423e9a4dedf194, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: "And that thing you\u2019re carrying? It reacts to them. Means you\u2019re
      not completely hopeless."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dfd49278aaeff4b4a9423e9a4dedf194, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d01bd1b437def094c9a6780dbdad5281, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: I need Xenocore Elements to activate an Elyndari temple. Cutie help me.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a732a571f82d164eaae6405497a3c69, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dfd49278aaeff4b4a9423e9a4dedf194, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 40eddda1543e24346865a91cacd547f2, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: "So you\u2019re heading to the temple. Figures."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 19b79383905171c41b80cd4bec17b504, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 40eddda1543e24346865a91cacd547f2, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: "If you stop calling me cute, maybe I\u2019ll show you where to start."
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1a1f0c89fd2ad8f488fa25619df9f084, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 40eddda1543e24346865a91cacd547f2, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Kaelaris
    text: No promises.
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9a732a571f82d164eaae6405497a3c69, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.06
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 19b79383905171c41b80cd4bec17b504, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 1
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ae6777ac6a52f3340b37a7632bbd4eb9, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  - speakerName: Rift
    text: Come on, sync-girl. Grab some Xenocore before something out here decides
      you look cute too. Trade me for anything!
    voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3a600993eb3c1184cabb4a91cbafa7c9, type: 3}
    typingSpeed: 0.03
    showOptionsHere: 0
    jumpBackToPreviousDialogue: 0
    previousDialogueLineIndex: 0
    speakerSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 19b79383905171c41b80cd4bec17b504, type: 3}
    isLeftSpeaker: 0
    leftPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ae6777ac6a52f3340b37a7632bbd4eb9, type: 3}
    customFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 84c1d05c69deacd4cb1362b81cba58e6, type: 2}
  options: []
  isFinalDialogue: 0
